deck: An Academy Award nominated American actor notable for his roles in films such as The Social Network and Now You See Me. Eisenberg is set to play Superman's arch nemesis Lex Luthor in the Man of Steel sequel titled Batman vs. Superman: Dawn of Justice.
description:
Jesse Eisenberg first began acting prominence in the 2009 comedy film Adventureland, where he starred in the main role. Eisenberg also played a main prominent role in the successful zombie-comedy film Zombieland.

Eisenberg's most acclaimed role was in the 2010 film The Social Network where he starred as real life Facebook founder Mark Zuckerberg. The film was a massive success both critically and commercially, as the film was nominated for eight Academy Awards (and won three), including a best actor nomination for Eisenberg. Eisenberg also recently starred in the movie Now You See Me alongside Mark Ruffalo, Isla Fisher, Woody Harrelson, Dave Franco, and Morgan Freeman.

Eisenberg is set to star in the upcoming Man of Steel sequel titled Batman vs. Superman: Dawn of Justice opposite of Henry Cavill as Superman's arch nemesis Lex Luthor. The film is slated to come out on March 25th of 2016.
name: Jesse Eisenberg

deck: An Israeli actress set to portray Wonder Woman in the upcoming Batman vs Superman: Dawn of Justice movie.
description: Gadot first began a career as a model, before landing a minor role in the Fast and Furious movies. She was later cast in her first major role as Wonder Woman/Diana Prince in the upcoming Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice movie alongside Henry Cavill returning in his role as Superman/Clark Kent, Ben Affleck as Batman/Bruce Wayne, and Jesse Eisenberg as Superman's arch nemesis Lex Luthor. The film is set for release on March 25th, 2016.
name: Gal Gadot
